97
00:04:16,489 --> 00:04:19,592
If I really try to break you two up…

98
00:04:19,659 --> 00:04:20,627
You bastard!

99
00:04:20,693 --> 00:04:21,527
<i>It's fine.</i>

100
00:04:21,594 --> 00:04:23,763
It doesn't matter how much you oppose it.

101
00:04:24,264 --> 00:04:26,566
My name might mean "yield,"
but I will never yield.

102
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:29,702
I'm the champion of Roppongi, after all.

103
00:04:31,504 --> 00:04:33,239
Father, do you see?

104
00:04:33,306 --> 00:04:34,974
Please believe me.

105
00:04:36,209 --> 00:04:38,111
Eventually, Nagisacchi will be born,

106
00:04:38,945 --> 00:04:40,613
and Junko and I will pass away.

107
00:04:41,481 --> 00:04:42,315
