153
00:07:13,099 --> 00:07:14,600
No need. I'll see him anyway.

154
00:07:14,667 --> 00:07:16,302
And he's not that special to me.

155
00:07:17,904 --> 00:07:19,372
Please send Kiyoshi back.

156
00:07:19,872 --> 00:07:22,842
Even if he hates it and you have to use
force, put him on the bus.

157
00:07:22,909 --> 00:07:23,743
Right.

158
