183
00:08:55,701 --> 00:08:56,536
Huh?

184
00:09:05,344 --> 00:09:10,683
SCHOOL-6-URA

185
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,794
Welcome to Showa.

186
00:09:22,662 --> 00:09:23,529
Well?

187
00:09:24,864 --> 00:09:25,932
It stinks.

188
00:09:26,599 --> 00:09:28,501
Stinks? That's a first.

189
00:09:29,936 --> 00:09:32,104
Well, you'll get used to it.

190
00:10:14,113 --> 00:10:15,514
Nagisa!

191
00:10:16,082 --> 00:10:18,150
-Junko, how have you been?
-Great.

192
00:10:18,217 --> 00:10:19,418
I'm coming in.

193
00:10:31,864 --> 00:10:32,765
