194
00:10:33,466 --> 00:10:34,300
Grandma?

195
00:10:34,934 --> 00:10:36,602
No, that's my mom.

196
00:10:37,136 --> 00:10:39,405
He's my geezer's wife,
but she's not an old woman.

197
00:10:40,039 --> 00:10:41,774
She passed away at 35, after all.

198
00:10:42,842 --> 00:10:44,110
-Where are you going?
-Uh…

199
00:10:44,176 --> 00:10:45,244
Just going for a smoke.

200
