You couldn't have hanky-panky with Junko,

256
00:13:21,100 --> 00:13:23,068
but you saw boobs on terrestrial TV.

257
00:13:23,135 --> 00:13:24,170
Aren't you craving

258
00:13:24,236 --> 00:13:26,338
a Mango Frappuccino from Starbucks?

259
00:13:32,545 --> 00:13:33,379
