260
00:13:35,181 --> 00:13:36,015
Well,

261
00:13:36,081 --> 00:13:37,817
the bus leaves at 3:55 p.m.

262
00:13:37,883 --> 00:13:39,118
So say bye to your friends.

263
00:13:39,685 --> 00:13:40,920
Here you go.

264
00:13:40,986 --> 00:13:42,288
Please enjoy.

265
00:13:43,289 --> 00:13:45,191
-Let's dig in.
-Let's dig in.

